def main():
    data_processor = DataProcessor()
    data_processor.process_deletions("2022-01-01")

    fabs_updater = FABSUpdater()
    fabs_updater.update_fabs_records()

    ui_designer = UIDesigner()

    ui_designer.track_tech_thursday_issues()
    ui_designer.begin_user_testing()
    ui_designer.schedule_user_testing("2022-01-01")

    dev_ops_engineer = DevOpsEngineer()
    dev_ops_engineer.provide_new_relic_data()

    broker_user = BrokerUser()
    broker_user.sync_d1_file_generation()
    broker_user.update_sql_codes()
    broker_user.add_ppopcode_cases()
    broker_user.derive_funding_agency_code()
    broker_user.map_federal_action_obligation()
    broker_user.validate_ppopzip4()

    developer = Developer()
    developer.index_domain_models()
    developer.update_broker_validation_rule_table()
    developer.clarify_cfda_error_code()
    developer.update_fabs_sample_file()
    developer.prevent_duplicate_transactions()
    developer.load_historical_fpds_data()
    developer.determine_best_way_to_load_historical_fpds_data()

    fabs_user = FABSUser()
    fabs_user.access_frontend_urls()
    fabs_user.download_uploaded_fabs_file("Sample file ID")
    fabs_user.view_submitted_data()

    tester = Tester()
    tester.test_features_in_non_staging_environments()

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
